instanceVariables.text:
The room behind the door has no energy, so you must plug 3 fuses in the generator to restore it. Since it is dark in there, you'll need to get a high-tech mask in the toolbox to proceed.

How to play:
[WASD] moves the character
[E] interacts with objects
[Mouse] looks around
[Space] toggles mask
Press [E] to get the high-tech mask
Press [E] to place fuse in generator
